786
01:08:08,063 --> 01:08:09,155
<i>I feel fear...</i>

787
01:08:10,398 --> 01:08:12,525
<i>...for the last time.</i>

788
01:08:28,750 --> 01:08:31,082
<i>A token funeral is held.</i>

789
01:08:31,419 --> 01:08:33,410
