832
01:12:03,298 --> 01:12:08,292
<i>A very young girl looks at me and smiles.</i>

833
01:12:09,070 --> 01:12:11,061
<i>She's beautiful.</i>

834
01:12:11,973 --> 01:12:17,969
<i>After each long kiss, she plants a smaller,
